leve.name: Leaves Much to Be Desired
leve.description: The mission of the East Aldenard Trading Company is more than simply making a profit. Ours is the work of fulfilling Eastern fantasies with our offering of exotic spices and mysterious reagents, opening the minds of our patrons through the doors of trade...and also making a profit in the process. We are always on the lookout for greenery that might grow our business.
leve.client: East Aldenard Trading Company Associate, Kikimo Kimo
